    "Content": "\n> [!NOTE]\n> Access from the default network namespace is done using the VPN network namespace address.\\\n> `curl 192.168.15.1:9091`\n\nSee all options and their descriptions in the [module file](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Maroka-chan/VPN-Confinement/master/modules/options.nix).\n",
